Properties.Name: values
Properties.Description: The facet ranges to produce. The values must be listed in ascending order to get the expected results. For example, values=10,20 produces three buckets: one for base rate 0 up to but not including 10, one for 10 up to but not including 20, and one for 20 and higher.
